      <lg xml:id="KC6">
<l>iṉṟu toṭṭum eḻumaiyum empirāṉ</l>
<l>niṉṟu taṉpukaḻ ētta aruḷiṉāṉ</l>
<l>kuṉṟa māṭat tiruk kurukūr nampi</l>
<l>eṉṟum eṉṉai ikaḻvu ilaṉ kāṇmiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Beginning today and for seven successive births,</l>
<l>Our Lord has graced [me] to perpetually sing his praise.</l>
<l>See the Lord of Tirukkurukūr with mountain [high] mansions</l>
<l>who never scorns me!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
